➢ Environment and Social Standards ESS1: The Environment Audit
➢ Environment and Social Standards ESS1: Strategic Environment and Social Assessment (SESA)
➢ Project Monitoring, Supervision and Reporting
➢ Resource Efficiency and Pollution Prevention and Management
➢ Preparation of Pollution Plans
➢ Environmental Compliance Monitoring and Enforcement
➢ Community Health and Safety (ESS4)
➢ Environmental Health Assessment (EAH)
➢ Biodiversity Conservation and Sustainable Management of Living Resources (ESS6)
➢ Natural Resources and Wildlife Conservation and Land Use in Nigeria
➢ Cultural Heritage (ESS8)
➢ Stakeholder Engagement Plan (ESS10) Module 2
Selected Topics in Environmental Standards
➢ Overview of Air Quality Management
➢ Global Environmental Change
➢ Integrated Water Resources Management (IWRM)
➢ Water Quality Assessment
➢ Wastewater Management
➢ Wastewater Reuse in agriculture and irrigation
