The Advanced Certificate (TRACK B) programme will be delivered within 3 weeks of pedagogic interaction. HOW TO APPLY
Candidates are kindly advised to visit CIPESS website: www.cipessfuam.edu.ng and complete the online application form to register for their preferred courses MODE OF DELIVERY
➢ Onsite interactions and online LOCATIONS
➢ Mini Lecture Theatres 1,3 & 4, College of Forestry and Fisheries, JOSTUM.
➢ Customized  training would be available  in designated  CIPESS  study Centers  in  all six North Central States for interested persons
➢ Custom-made training is available on request to meet the specific requirements of any organization.
➢ Staff Development Center, Makurdi.
➢ Joint Universities Preliminary Examinations Board (JUPEB), FUAM Annex, Makurdi PARTICIPANTS’ CHARGES
Nigerian candidates for the regular short courses would be required to pay the highly subsidized charges of thirty-one thousand five hundred naira  (N31,500)  only per menu.  Non-Nigerian candidates would be required to pay one hundred and fifty USD ($150). Scholarships are available for qualified candidates. CONTACT US
